		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">木盾丘丘持盾朝玩家进行冲击，触碰造成<span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>伤害，冲击后甩盾，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害。该</span><span textDecoration="underline">木盾</span><span color="#99ffb2">可再生</span><span>。并且会拍灭燃烧的木盾。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="421" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffbfbf">(无盾)<span color="#ffffff">木盾丘丘愤怒拳击两下后冲向玩家，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">50%,100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，最后飞扑过去，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="426" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffbfbf">(无盾)<span color="#ffffff">木盾丘丘从地里抓出一个草史莱姆，击碎，然后木盾丘丘就有了新的</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffffff">木盾</span><span color="#ffffff">。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/木盾丘丘暴徒.assets/Image_13.png')" x="719" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/木盾丘丘暴徒.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="425">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/木盾丘丘暴徒.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="714">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/木盾丘丘暴徒.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1392" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="421" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">木盾丘丘使用右手进行1段的攻击。<br/><span color="#ffb299">有盾：</span><span>带盾进行挥舞，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#ffb299">无盾：</span><span>挥右手，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">木盾丘丘从地里挖出草史莱姆丢出，但造成<span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#96673d" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#96673d">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
